%20Wins%20Wrestling%20Federation%20Poll%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20his%20close%20aide%20swept%20the%20elections%20to%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%2C%20the%20body's%20former%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20some%20of%20India's%20top%20wrestlers%2C%20declared%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Edabdaba%20tha%2C%20dabdaba%20rahega%3C%2Fem%3E%20(I%20prevailed%2C%20I%20will%20prevail)%26quot%3B%2C%20indicating%20that%20his%20dominance%20would%20continue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrij%20Bhushan's%20aide%20Sanjay%20Singh%20got%2040%20out%20of%20the%2047%20votes%20in%20Thursday's%20election%2C%20defeating%20Commonwealth%20Games%20Gold%20medallist%20Anita%20Sheoran.%20Ms%20Sheoran%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdespite-controversies-brij-bhushans-aide-wins-wrestling-body-polls-4715507%5C%22%3Ebacked%20by%20wrestlers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20Sakshee%20Malikkh%2C%20Bajrang%20Punia%2C%20and%20Vinesh%20Phogat%2C%20who%20had%20protested%20against%20Brij%20Bhushan%2C%20a%20BJP%20MP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20election%20result%2C%20Brij%20Bhushan%20said%20it%20was%20a%20victory%20of%20the%20country's%20wrestlers%20and%20that%20he%20hoped%20wrestling%20activities%20which%20were%20%26quot%3Bstopped%20for%2011%20months%26quot%3B%20-%20since%20the%20protests%20against%20him%20began%20-%20would%20now%20resume.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20MP%20also%20called%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20who%20has%20said%20he%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbrij-bhushan-wfi-polls-wfi-victory-of-truth-over-lies-brij-bhushan-aide-on-wrestling-body-polls-4716036%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bdefinitely%20close%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20former%20wrestling%20federation%20chief%2C%20a%20non-partisan%20person.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20message%20has%20been%20given.%20Every%20%3Cem%3Eakhaada%3C%2Fem%3E%20(wrestling%20academy)%20in%20the%20country%20is%20bursting%20firecrackers.%20%3Cem%3EDabdabaa%20tha%2C%20dabdabaa%20rahega%3C%2Fem%3E!%20I%20want%20to%20give%20the%20credit%20of%20victory%20to%20the%20wrestlers%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20electors.%20I%20want%20to%20thank%20the%20government%20as%20well.%20The%20elections%20were%20done%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court...%20the%20Centre%20went%20ahead%20to%20make%20sure%20elections%20happened%20and%20a%20non-partisan%20person%20was%20chosen%20as%20president%2C%26quot%3B%20Brij%20Bhushan%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20%3Cem%3E'grahan'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(eclipse)%20of%2011%20months%20on%20wrestling%20is%20over.%20Within%2010%20days%2C%20the%20landscape%20of%20wrestling%20will%20change%20again%20and%20we%20will%20perform%20in%20the%20Olympics%20the%20way%20people%20want%20us%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMallikh%20Quits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20Sanjay%20Singh's%20election%2C%20which%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20continuity%20of%20leadership%20in%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%2C%20Olympic%20medallist%20Sakshee%20Mallikh%20put%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsakshee-malikkh-says-will-quit-wrestling-after-ex-chiefs-aide-wins-federation-polls-4716170%5C%22%3Eboots%20on%20a%20table%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20a%20press%20briefing%20and%20said%20that%20she%20is%20quitting%20the%20sport.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Malikkh%20said%20the%20wrestlers%20had%20wanted%20a%20woman%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20wrestling%20federation.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BBut%20that%20did%20not%20happen%E2%80%A6%20We%20fought%2C%20but%20if%20the%20new%20president%20is%20Brij%20Bhushan's%20aide%2C%20his%20business%20partner%2C%20then%20I%20quit%20wrestling.%26quot%3B%20She%20also%20broke%20down%20as%20she%20was%20leaving%20the%20venue%20of%20the%20press%20conference.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Ms%20Mallikh%20quitting%2C%20Brij%20Bhushan%20told%20ANI%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%20Phogat%2C%20who%20also%20broke%20into%20tears%20at%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20said%20women%20wrestlers%20will%20continue%20to%20face%20harassment%20and%20she%20has%20no%20clue%20%E2%80%9Chow%20to%20find%20justice%20in%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20future%20of%20our%20wrestling%20career%20is%20in%20the%20dark.%20We%20do%20not%20know%20where%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Victory%20of%20Truth'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Singh%20called%20his%20election%20as%20president%20of%20the%20wrestling%20federation%20a%20victory%20of%20truth%20over%20lies%20and%2C%20in%20a%20reference%20to%20Brij%20Bhushan%2C%20he%20said%20an%20attempt%20was%20made%20to%20tarnish%20the%20reputation%20of%20a%20person%20whose%20character%20was%20spotless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20his%20supporters%20congratulated%20him%2C%20slogans%20were%20also%20raised%20in%20Hindi%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3ESanjay%20Bhayya%20kya%20lekar%20chale%2C%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%20ke%20khadau%20lekar%20chale%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Where%20is%20Sanjay%20Singh%20going%3F%20He%20is%20carrying%20Brij%20Bhushan's%20wooden%20footwear)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20president%2C%20a%20senior%20vice-president%2C%20four%20vice-presidents%2C%20a%20secretary-general%2C%20a%20treasurer%2C%20two%20joint%20secretaries%20and%20five%20executive%20members%20of%20the%20wrestling%20body%20were%20also%20elected.%20Most%20of%20the%20people%20who%20secured%20these%20posts%20are%20also%20seen%20as%20belonging%20to%20the%20Brij%20Bhushan%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703165460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F6djondcg_brij-bhushan-sanjay-singh-pti-650_650x400_21_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fb