%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fbyron-allen-allen-media-group-board-six-new-members-1235848494%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Quit%26quot%3B%3A%20Wrestlers%20Weep%20After%20Controversial%20Candidate%20Wins%20Key%20Poll%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20an%20aide%20of%20former%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20succeeded%20him%20in%20the%20top%20post%20in%20elections%20held%20today%2C%20Olympic%20medallist%20and%20ace%20wrestler%20Sakshee%20Malikkh%20declared%20that%20she%20is%20quitting%20the%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Singh%20is%20a%20long-time%20aide%20of%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20WFI%20chief%20for%2012%20years.%20A%20six-time%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20had%20to%20step%20aside%20after%20top%20wrestlers%2C%20including%20Ms%20Malikkh%2C%20accused%20him%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20women%20wrestlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20today's%20elections%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%20won%2040%20out%20of%2047%20votes.%20Commonwealth%20Games%20gold%20medallist%20Anita%20Sheoran%2C%20the%20protesting%20wrestlers'%20choice%20for%20the%20post%20of%20WFI%20president%2C%20got%20just%20seven%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country's%20top%20wrestlers%2C%20Ms%20Malikkh%2C%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20Bajrang%20Punia%20expressed%20their%20disappointment%20at%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20into%20tears%20during%20an%20interaction%20with%20the%20media%2C%20Commonwealth%20and%20Asian%20Games%20Gold%20medallist%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%20that%20Sanjay%20Singh%20has%20been%20elected%20chief%20of%20the%20federation%2C%20women%20wrestlers%20will%20continue%20to%20face%20harassment.%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Phogat%20said%20she%20has%20%26quot%3Bno%20clue%20how%20to%20find%20justice%20in%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20future%20of%20our%20wrestling%20career%20is%20in%20the%20dark.%20We%20do%20not%20know%20where%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Punia%2C%20an%20Olympic%20bronze%20medallist%2C%20said%20it%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bgovernment's%20promise%20to%20us%20was%20not%20fulfilled%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20linked%20to%20any%20party%2C%20we%20did%20not%20come%20here%20for%20politics.%20We%20were%20fighting%20for%20truth%2C%20but%20today%20an%20aide%20of%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20has%20become%20the%20WFI%20president%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Malikkh%20said%20they%20had%20wanted%20the%20wrestling%20body%20to%20get%20a%20woman%20chief.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that%20did%20not%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe%20fought%2C%20but%20if%20the%20new%20president%20is%20Brij%20Bhushan's%20aide%2C%20his%20business%20partner%2C%20then%20I%20quit%20wrestling%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Olympic%20bronze%20medallist%20said%2C%20putting%20her%20boots%20on%20the%20table.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20this%20year%2C%20the%20three%20wrestlers%20led%20a%20huge%20protest%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%2C%20accusing%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20several%20wrestlers%20and%20demanding%20action%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20called%20off%20their%20protest%20after%20the%20government%20ordered%20a%20probe.%20The%20wrestlers%20were%20also%20assured%20that%20no%20aide%20or%20relative%20of%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20would%20be%20allowed%20to%20contest%20the%20next%20polls%20of%20the%20wrestling%20body.%20While%20Brij%20Bhushan's%20son%20Prateek%20and%20son-in-law%20Vishal%20Singh%20did%20not%20enter%20the%20poll%20contest%2C%20his%20aide%20Sanjay%20Singh's%20nomination%20was%20cleared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Singh%20has%20earlier%20served%20as%20vice-president%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20wrestling%20body.%20He%20was%20part%20of%20the%20WFI's%C2%A0last%20executive%20council%20and%20its%20joint%20secretary%20since%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20victory%20in%20today's%20elections%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%20said%20it%20was%20a%20win%20of%20truth%20over%20lies.%20%26quot%3BThey%20levelled%20such%20allegations%20against%20a%20person%20whose%20character%20does%20not%20have%20a%20place%20for%20those%20traits%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0On%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20he%20is%20close%20to%20the%20BJP%20MP%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20no%20doubt%20I%20am%20close%20to%20him.%26quot%3B%20Asked%20about%20concerns%20of%20a%20section%20of%20wrestlers%20about%20how%20the%20federation%20would%20function%20now%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20no%20injustice%20against%20any%20woman%20wrestler.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sanjay%20Singh's%20victory%2C%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20give%20the%20credit%20of%20victory%20to%20the%20wrestlers%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20secretary%20of%20WFI.%20I%20hope%20that%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20new%20federation%2C%20wrestling%20events%20will%20resume.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20for%20the%20WFI%20election%20began%20in%20July%2C%20but%20court%20cases%20kept%20delaying%20it.%20This%20led%20to%20the%20international%20wrestling%20body%20suspending%20WFI.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20recently%20set%20aside%20a%20stay%20imposed%20by%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%2C%20clearing%20the%20decks%20for%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703162820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fjlq4i73_sakshi-malik_625x300_21_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsakshee-malikkh-says-will-quit-wrestling-after-ex-chiefs-aide-wins-federation-polls-4716170%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shortly%20after%20an%20aide%20of%20former%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2