n%3EWikipedia%2C%20with%20absolute%20indelicacy%2C%20defines%20old%20age%20as%20%E2%80%9Cages%20nearing%20or%20surpassing%20the%20life%20expectancy%20of%20human%20beings%20and%20is%20thus%20the%20end%20of%20the%20human%20cycle.%E2%80%9D%20Reinforcing%20this%20sombre%20hypothesis%2C%20neuroscience%20suggests%20that%20the%20brain%20volume%20diminishes%20over%20time%20at%20the%20rate%20of%205%25%20every%20decade%20from%20the%2030s%2C%20especially%20that%20part%20of%20the%20brain%20that%20regulates%20executive%20functions%20and%20leadership%20qualities%20such%20as%20problem-solving%20or%20goal%20setting.%20The%20decline%20in%20aptitude%20and%20mental%20processing%20speed%20results%20in%20unconscious%20repetition%20of%20thoughts%20and%20behaviour%20and%20an%20erratic%20memory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20one%20who%20has%20been%20there%20for%20some%20time%2C%20I%20can%20assure%20you%20that%20old%20age%20is%20not%20a%20nice%20place%20to%20be.%20Tactfully%20but%20infelicitously%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20golden%20or%20senior%20years%2C%20the%20twilight%20age%20is%20a%20litany%20of%20aches%20and%20pains%2C%20memory%20loss%20and%20a%20lot%20more.%20O%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eld%20age%20is%20a%20burden%20not%20only%20for%20the%20dotard%20but%20also%20for%20those%20trapped%20in%20his%20orbit.%20And%20if%20the%20decrepit%20old%20guy%20happens%20to%20be%20a%20powerful%20politician%2C%20watch%20out%20because%20he%20is%20up%20to%20no%20good.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPoliticians%20are%20unquestionably%20one%20species%20who%20wear%20badly%3B%20the%20older%20they%20get%2C%20the%20worse%20they%20become.%20Our%20world%20is%20being%20ruined%20by%20malevolent%20old%20politicians%20who%20preach%20high%20principle%20but%20act%20dishonourably.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20octogenarian%20US%20President%2C%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20and%20the%20unspeakable%20septuagenarian%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Israel%2C%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20are%20