o%20cast%20aside%20if%20re-elected)%2C%20our%20benighted%20country%20is%20firmly%20under%20the%20authoritarian%20leadership%20of%20the%20Vishwaguru%2C%20who%20is%20two-and-a-half%20times%20as%20old%20as%20the%20median%20Indian%20(28%20years).%20In%20his%20imperious%20whip%20hand%2C%20our%20decorative%20democracy%20is%20a%20sham%20behind%20which%20this%20regime%20has%20captured%20every%20institution%20of%20governance%2C%20using%20fear%20and%20dissimulation%20as%20the%20controlling%20mechanisms.%20%E2%80%9CKilling%20the%20Constitution%20by%20a%20million%20cuts%E2%80%9D%20is%20professor%20Tarunabh%20Khaitan%E2%80%99s%20brilliant%20forensic%20dissection%20of%20how%20our%20freedoms%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Cpicked%E2%80%9D%20even%20as%20we%20sleepwalk%20into%20authoritarianism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20his%20law-enforcement%20hitmen%20besiege%20and%20batter%20all%20opponents%20into%20submission%2C%20the%20preening%20Vishwaguru%20pulls%20the%20wool%20over%20our%20adoring%20eyes.%20The%20sententious%20leader%20effortlessly%20straddles%20the%20disjunction%20between%20precept%20and%20practice.%20He%20speaks%20out%20against%20corruption%20unfazed%20by%20his%20fingerprints%20on%20Adani-gate%2C%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20washing%20machine-transformed%20opponents-turned-friends.%20He%20boasts%20about%20being%20the%20fifth%20largest%20economy%20%E2%80%93%20disregarding%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20terms%20of%20per%20capita%20GDP%20we%20are%20ranked%20127%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20out%20of%20179%20countries.%20He%20hits%20out%20at%20dynasts%20even%20as%20all%20institutions%20have%20been%20usurped%20by%20a%20single%20family%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%20%E2%80%93%20and%20parades%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eghar%20me%20guskar%20maroonga%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Emacho%20image%20but%20cringing%20away%20from%20China%20which%2C%20uninvited%2C%20enjoys%20our%20hospitality.%20And%20never%20tires%20of%20repeating%20the%20bogus%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESabka%20saath%20sabka%20vikas%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Etrope%20despite%20doing%20everything%20to%20divide%20his%20people%20to%20stay%20in%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20from%20the%20looks%20of%20it%20%E2%80%93%20his%20god-like%20power%20over%20his%20people%2C%20his%20abuse%20of%20religion%20to%20divide%20and%20rule%2C%20%E2%80%98his%E2%80%99%20emphatic%20victory%20in%20the%20recent%20Assembly%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20our%20Vishwaguru%20threatens%20to%20be%20the%20Methuselah%20among%20world%20leaders!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMathew%20John%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant.%20The%20views%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703161859000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21174149%2FCopy-of-Lead-image-size-5.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fare-aging-politicians-up-to-the-task-of-solving-global-issues%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Our%20world%20is%20being%20ruined%20by%20malevolent%20old%20politicians%20who%20preach%20high%20principle%20but%20act%20dishonourably.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fare-aging-politicians-up-to-the-task-of-solving-global-issues%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tabu%20feels%202023%20has%20passed%20in%20a%20blink%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703161791000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106186111%2Cimgsize-34326.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftabu-feels-2023-has-passed-in-a-blink-the-actress-asks-fans-what-they-think-see-inside%2Farticleshow%2F106186111.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%2