20his%20600%2C000%20or%20so%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Qatar%20staff%20asked%20him%20to%20take%20down%20the%20video%20%E2%80%94%20and%20when%20he%20did%20not%2C%20seemed%20to%20retaliate%20by%20canceling%20a%20future%20booking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20the%20move%20as%20%26quot%3Bdrastic%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Ba%20worrying%20example%20of%20censorship.%26quot%3B%20Qatar%20Airlines%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20record%20when%20approach%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Cahill's%20August%20video%20he%20said%20Qatar%20was%20losing%20its%20title%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F20-best-airlines-in-the-world-skytrax-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworld's%20best%20airline%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20cited%20%26quot%3Boutdated%20planes%2C%20dirty%20cabins%2C%20unfriendly%2C%20and%20demotivated%20crew%2C%20and%20running%20out%20of%20food%20choices%26quot%3B%20as%20some%20of%20his%20qualms%20while%20documenting%20his%20trip%20from%20Colombo%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20to%20the%20airline's%20hub%20in%20Doha%2C%20Qatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20amassed%20over%20600%2C000%20views%20and%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20Qatar%20Airways%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECahill%20posted%20another%20video%20on%20December%2016%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20airline%20got%20in%20contact%20with%20him%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20take%20down%20the%20video%2C%20offering%20a%20free%20flight%20if%20he%20complied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20video%2C%20Cahill%20said%20he%20refused%2C%20prompting%20Qatar%20to%20instead%20ask%20him%20to%20remove%20any%20negative%20comments%20other%20people%20posted%20on%20his%20video.%20He%20turned%20that%20down%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECahill%20said%20in%20the%20video%20he%20also%20received%20an%20email%20from%20a%20staff%20member%20on%20the%20flight%20he%20filmed%2C%20saying%20she%20had%20not%20given%20him%20permission%20to%20record%20her.%20She%20later%20told%20him%20she%20feared%20she%