lming%20my%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20things%20changed%20after%20I%20posted%20a%20rather%20negative%20but%20still%20balanced%20review.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20many%20of%20his%20viewer%20appeared%20to%20have%20decided%20not%20to%20fly%20with%20Qatar%20given%20how%20it%20treated%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECahill%20said%2C%20though%2C%20that%20he%20hoped%20that%20Qatar%20might%20change%20its%20attitude%20given%20that%20it%20recently%20got%20a%20new%20CEO%2C%20Badr%20Mohammed%20Al-Meer%2C%20who%20has%20said%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fqatar-airways-new-ceo-wants-culture-of-trust-and-empowerment-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewants%20to%20bring%20a%20culture%20of%20%26quot%3Btrust%20and%20empowerment%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20airline%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20has%20faced%20a%20string%20of%20controversies.%20In%202018%2C%20its%20former%20CEO%20said%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fqatar-airways-ceo-akbar-al-baker-says-woman-couldnt-do-his-job-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewoman%20couldn't%20do%20his%20job%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20it%20is%20a%20very%20challenging%20position.%26quot%3B%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20a%20former%20flight%20attendant%20said%20he%20was%20fired%20from%20the%20airline%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fqatar-airways-flight-attendant-fired-hermes-tinted-moisturizer-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor%20using%20tinted%20moisturizer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutuber-says-qatar-airways-banned-him-after-negative-review-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703160162000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6584266fa79e5746976c1419%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22origi