ress%20conference.%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20was%20proposed%20as%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20for%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20by%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20This%20fourth%20meeting%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20was%20held%20to%20discuss%20modes%20of%20campaigning%20and%20seat-sharing%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar%20is%20upset%20at%20INDIA%20partners%20for%20not%20handing%20the%20post%20of%20convenor%20straightaway%20to%20its%20chief%2C%20given%20his%20experience%20as%20the%20longest-serving%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20the%20alliance.%20Senior%20JDU%20members%20have%20demanded%20that%20Mr%20Kumar%20be%20declared%20the%20PM%20candidate%20not%20only%20for%20his%20seniority%20but%20also%20for%20what%20they%20call%20his%20appeal%20and%20charisma%2C%20matching%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's.%20Moreover%2C%20they%20say%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20was%20the%20one%20who%20fronted%20moves%20that%20crystallised%20into%20a%20pan-India%20opposition%20alliance%20INDIA%2C%20demonstrating%20his%20commitment%20to%20fighting%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20reject%20the%20very%20idea%20of%20INDIA%20alliance%20ever%20since%20its%20formation.%20That's%20why%20they%20are%20spreading%20rumours%20and%20counter-narratives%20every%20time.%20Lalu%20Yadav%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20are%20the%20architects%20of%20opposition%20unity%20to%20dismantle%20an%20undemocratic%20government%20led%20by%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Nawal%20Kishore%2C%20RJD%20national%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20right%20after%20the%20fourth%20alliance%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%2C%20JDU%20MP%20Sunil%20Kumar%20Pintu%2C%20taking%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20funds%20crunch%2C%20said%20the%20get-together%20was%20%26quot%3Brestricted%20to%20tea%20and%20biscuits%20without%20samosa%20and%20without%20any%20discussions%20on%20any%20serious%20issue%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20context%2C%20Mr%20Pintu%20had%20praised%20PM%20Modi's%20leadership%20after%20the%20BJP's%20win%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApparently%2C%20the%20reason%20behind%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20sulk%20is%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20proposed%20Mr%20Kharge's%20name%20as%20the%20opposition's%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20for%202024.%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20seconded%20the%20proposal.%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20the%20alliance%20should%20first%20concentrate%20on%20winning%20elections%3B%20the%20PM%20pick%20could%20be%20decided%20later.%20Sources%20say%20both%20Ms%20Banerjee%20and%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20named%20Mr%20Kharge%2C%20believing%20that%20as%20a%20Dalit%20face%2C%20he%20could%20help%20the%20alliance%20pull%20in%20Scheduled%20Caste%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20KC%20Tyagi%2C%20the%20JDU's%20national%20spokesperson%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNeither%20Nitish%20Kumar%20nor%20Laly%20Yadav%20or%20our%20parties%20have%20publicly%20proposed%20any%20motion%20favouring%20Mr%20Kumar%20as%20the%20convenor%20of%20INDIA%20alliance%20or%20its%20Prime%20Ministerial%20face.%20Even%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20meeting%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20it%20was%20not%20discussed.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20surprise%20at%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20move%2C%20Mr%20Tyagi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20how%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20proposed%20Mr%20Kharge's%20name.%20In%20our%20opinion%2C%20we%20should%20jointly%20focus%20on%20winning%20the%20magic%20number%20of%20272%20seats%20and%20then%20meet%20to%20decide%20on%20who%20will%20be%20Prime%20Minister.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20say%20it%20was%20at%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20instance%20that%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20pitched%20and%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20backed%20Mr%20Kharge's%20name.%20It%20was%20a%20strategic%20move%20aimed%20at%20two%20targets%2C%20they%20say.%20First%2C%20Lalu%20Yadav%20wanted%20to%20cut%20down%20Mr%20Kumar%20politically.%20Secondly%2C%20the%20BJP%20wanted%20a%20Modi%20versus%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20fight%2C%20which%20would%20have%20been%20a%20predictable%20no-brainer.%20Lalu%20Yadav%2C%20sources%20say%2C%20wants%20it%20to%20be%20a%20Modi%20versus%20Kharge%20showdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JDU%20has%20announced%20a%20national%20executive%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%20on%20December%2029.%20It%20has%20called%20its%20national%20council%20meeting%20on%20the%20same%20day%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20may%20address%20the%20party%20amid%20fresh%20rumblings.%20Sources%20say%20Mr%20Kumar%20may%20open%20up%20about%20his%20displeasure%20with%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20in%20the%20meeting%20and%20even%20chalk%20out%20a%20new%20course%20for%20himself%20and%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20was%20silent%20for%20a%20while%20and%20Mr%20Kumar%20too%20had%20voiced%20his%20frustration%20at%20the%20soporific%20pace%20of%20strategy%20in%20the%20bloc%20until%20recently.%20The%20Congress%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20were%20busy%20fighting%20each%20other%20in%20assembly%20elections%2C%20both%20apparently%20forgetting%20their%20shared%20pledge%20from%20three%20previous%20meetings.%20Perhaps%20seeing%20himself%20as%20the%20face%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20actively%20pursued%20the%20INDIA%20alliance's%20cause%2C%20addressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Jharkhand%20last%20month.%20He%20is%20also%20scheduled%20to%20hold%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20an%20assembly%20segment%20that%20falls%20in%20PM%20Modi's%20parliamentary%20constituency%20Varanasi.%20Other%20than%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20was%20also%20looking%20at%20travelling%20to%20Maharashtra%20and%20Haryana%20for%20rallies%2C%20on%20the%20invitation%20of%20caste-based%20federations.%20These%20plans%20may%20just%20fade%20away%20after%20the%20latest%20INDIA%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20yet%20to%20recover%20from%20its%201%3A%203%20drubbing%20in%20recent%20state%20elections%2C%20and%20its%20monumental%20loss%20of%20stature.%20Its%20bargaining%20power%20among%20opposition%20parties%20has%20nosedived.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20other%20parties%20have%20started%20asserting%20themselves%20more.%20Mr%20Kharge's%20name%20is%20one%20such%20gimmick.%20Mr%20Yadav%20wants%20his%20son%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Bihar%2C%20to%20replace%20Nitish%20Kumar%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%20After%20betrayals%20in%20the%20past%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20has%20a%20trust%20deficit%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Mr%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20perception%20was%20that%20Mr%20Kumar%20will%20be%20the%20PM%20face%20or%20convenor%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%20His%20party%20members%20wanted%20him%20to%20be%20PM.%20Similarly%2C%20people%20in%20the%20RJD%20want%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20to%20be%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20face%20of%20the%20'Mahagathbandhan'%20or%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Ravi%20Upadhyay%2C%20a%20senior%20journalist%20from%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JDU%20council%20meeting%2C%20featuring%20more%20than%20200%20members%2C%20must%20be%20keenly%20watched%20by%20both%20the%20ruling%20NDA%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20if%20only%20to%20see%20what%20Mr%20Kumar%20says.%20The%20lack%20of%20cohesion%20within%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20already%20started%20manifesting.%20Every%20party%20in%20the%20bloc%20has%20its%20own%20agenda.%20They%20are%20aware%20that%20divided%20they%20fall%3B%20individually%20they%20are%20weak%20and%20coming%20together%20is%20an%20imperative.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20strong%20narrative%2C%20their%20campaign%20is%20unlikely%20to%20ruffle%20the%20ruling%20party.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703159580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F2c8oogi8_nitish-kumar-lalu-yadav-mamata-banerjee-ani_625x300_21_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-nitish-kumar-lalu-yadav-resent-mamata-banerjees-move-4716225%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20INDIA%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%20on%20December%2019%20didn't%20go%20so%20well%20for%20the%20bloc%20with%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20RJD%20chief%20Lalu%20Yadav%20leaving%20without%20attending%20the%20much-anticipated%20press%20conference.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-nitish-kumar-lalu-yadav-resent-mamata-banerjees-move-4716225%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-nitish-kumar-lalu-yadav-resent-mamata-banerjees-move-4716225%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-nitish-kumar-lalu-yadav-resent-mamata-banerjees-move-4716225%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Northern%20Gaza%20no%20longer%20has%20a%20functional%20hospital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703159524000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106185118%2Cimgsize-2157406.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fnorthern-gaza-no-longer-has-a-functional-hospital%2Farticleshow%2F106184914.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106184914.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENorthern%20Gaza%20left%20without%20functional%20hospital%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20fuel%2C%20power%2C%20and%20medical%20supplies%3B%20Al-Ahli%20Hospital%20is%20minimally%20functional%2C%20treating%2