%20League.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CUEFA%20organises%20the%20competitions%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%20can%20reject%20other%20competitions%20%E2%80%93%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest%2C%E2%80%9D%20A22%20boss%20Bernd%20Reichart%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20the%20parties%20involved%20think%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20statement%20responding%20to%20the%20ruling%2C%20UEFA%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20ruling%20does%20not%20signify%20an%20endorsement%20or%20validation%20of%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98super%20league%E2%80%99%3B%20it%20rather%20underscores%20a%20pre-existing%20shortfall%20within%20UEFA%E2%80%99s%20pre-authorization%20framework%2C%20a%20technical%20aspect%20that%20has%20already%20been%20acknowledged%20and%20addressed%20in%20June%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2215%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CUEFA%20is%20confident%20in%20the%20robustness%20of%20its%20new%20rules%2C%20and%20specifically%20that%20they%20comply%20with%20all%20relevant%20European%20laws%20and%20regulations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2216%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20statement%20responding%20to%20the%20ruling%2C%20sports%20marketing%20agency%20A22%2C%20which%20represents%20those%20clubs%20still%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20Super%20League%2C%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2217%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20UEFA-monopoly%20is%20over.%20Football%20is%20free.%20Clubs%20are%20now%20free%20from%20the%20threat%20of%20sanction%20and%20free%20to%20determine%20their%20own%20futures.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2218%5C%22%3EA22%20CEO%20Bernd%20Reichart%20said%20new%20proposals%20for%20a%20Super%20League%20would%20be%20announced%20today%2C%20reported%20to%20be%20a%20midweek%20competition%20for%20both%20men%E2%80%99s%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20f