20next%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2243%5C%22%3EAs%20mentioned%20above%2C%20the%20ruling%20merely%20concerns%20the%20legality%20of%20UEFA%E2%80%99s%20market%20position%20within%20European%20Law.%20It%20does%20not%20necessarily%20give%20a%20European%20Super%20League%20the%20green%20light.%20The%20Grand%20Chamber%20judgment%E2%80%99s%20interpretation%20of%20EU%20law%20will%20now%20be%20passed%20back%20to%20the%20Madrid%20commercial%20court%20to%20make%20a%20decision%2C%20after%20the%20Spanish%20jurisdiction%20made%20the%20referral%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2243%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20there%20even%20appetite%20for%20a%20new%20European%20Super%20League%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2247%5C%22%3ESince%20the%20original%20breakaway%20attempt%20in%20April%202021%2C%20the%20European%20and%20global%20football%20landscape%20has%20changed%20somewhat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2248%5C%22%3EPartly%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20appease%20the%20Super%20League%20rebels%2C%20UEFA%20has%20signed%20off%20on%20a%20reformatted%20Champions%20League%20competition%20which%20will%20get%20underway%20next%20year.%20The%20traditional%20pre-Christmas%20group%20stage%20featuring%20several%20mini-leagues%20of%20four%20teams%20each%20is%20to%20be%20replaced%20by%20a%20%E2%80%9CSwiss%20model%E2%80%9D%C2%A0which%20will%20see%20all%20participating%20clubs%20compete%20in%20one%20single%20league%20table%2C%20playing%20more%20games%20against%20each%20other%2C%20before%20the%20majority%20of%20them%20progress%20to%20a%20knock-out%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2249%5C%22%3EIn%20England%20meanwhile%2C%20the%20Premier%20League%20has%20just%20announced%20a%20new%20domestic%20television%20rights%20deal%20worth%20a%20record%20%E2%82%AC7.73bn%20(%248.46bn)%20to%20its%20clubs.%20Any%20new%20Super%20League%20competition%20proposed%20by%20A22%20would%20have%20to%20be%20seriously%20lucrative%20to%20convince%20the%20top%20English%20clubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2250%5C%22%3EFurthermore%2C%20English%20football%E2%80%99s%20new%20%E2%80%9Cindependent%20regulator%E2%80%9D%C2%A0established%20by%20the%20UK%20government%20partly%20in%20response%20to%20the%20original%20Super%20League%20breakaway%20attempt%2C%20is%20set%20to%20forbid%20clubs%20from%20joining%20unapproved%20competitions%20under%20its%20licensing%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2251%5C%22%3EElsewhere%20in%20Europe%2C%20it%20has%20also%20been%20reported%20that%20CVC%2C%20the%20private%20equity%20firm%20which%20has%20recently%20invested%20in%20France%E2%80%99s%20Ligue%201%2C%20inserted%20a%20compensation%20clause%20into%20the%20deal%20to%20cover%20the%20eventuality%20of%20a%20French%20club%20participating%20in%20a%20new%20Super%20League.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2251%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%20German%20football%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2253%5C%22%3EIn%20Germany%2C%20club%20ownership%20structures%20also%20constitute%20a%20major%20obstacle.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20Federal%20Competition%20Regulator%20(Bundeskartellamt)%20recently%20concluded%20that%20the%20so-called%2050%2B1%20club%20ownership%20rule%2C%20which%20stipulates%20that%20members%20retain%20majority%20voting%20rights%20in%20clubs%20and%20thus%20prevents%20majority%20takeovers%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2254%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22safari-reader%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fbundesliga-deal-what-does-private-equity-want-in-football%2Fa-67732274%5C%22%3Edoes%20not%20contravene%20German%20competition%20law.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2255%5C%22%3EHowever%2C%20the%20ECJ%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20that%20UEFA%E2%80%99s%20dominant%20position%20within%20the%20European%20market%20effectively%20constitutes%20a%20monopoly%20could%20encourage%20opponents%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20data-reader-unique-id%3D%5C%2256%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22safari-reader%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fbundesliga-501-rule-set-to-stay-but-no-more-exemptions%2Fa-66232342%5C%22%3E50%2B1%20rule%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20take%20a%20similar%20case%20to%20the%20European%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20on%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flogs1279.xiti.com%2Fhit.xiti%3Fs%3D531599%26s2%3D2%26p%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%3A%3Athewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26di%3D%26an%3D%26ac%3D%26x1%3D1%26x2%3D2%26x5%3Dthewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26x6%3D1%26x8%3Den-VAS-Volltexte-JavaScript-thewire.in-dwde%26x10%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703158515000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21165943%2Femilio-garcia-AWdCgDDedH0-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Ffootball-eu-court-uefa-fifa-ban-european-super-league-unlawful%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20highly%20anticipated%20decision%20for%20football%20on%20the%20continent%2C%20the%20European%20Court%20of%20Justice%20has%20said%20UEFA%20and%20FIFA%20are%20guilty%20of%20abusing%20their%20dominant%20position.%20The%20court%20did%2C%20however%2C%20add%20that%20the%20ruling%20did%20not%20mean%20the%20Super%20League%20would%20be%20approved.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Ffootball-eu-court-uefa-fifa-ban-european-super-league-unlawful%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22First%2C%20the%20River%20Took%20Their%20Land.%20Then%20Came%20the%20Micro-Finance%20Companies.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21155111%2F%25E0%25A4%2595%25E0%25A4%25B0%25E0%25A5%258D%25E0%25A4%259C-%25E0%25A4%2595%25E0%25A5%2587-%25E0%25A4%25A6%25E0%25A4%25B8%25E0%25A5%258D%25E0%25A4%25A4%25E0%25A4%25BE%25E0%25A4%25B5%25E0%25A5%2587%25E0%25A4%259C%25E0%25A5%258B%25E0%25A4%2582-%25E0%25A4%2595%25E0%25A5%2587-%25E0%25A4%25B8%25E0%25A4%25BE%25E0%25A4%25A5-%25E0%25A4%25AE%25E0%25A4%25B9%25E0%25A4%25BF%25E0%25A4%25B2%25E0%25A4%25BE%25E0%25A4%25AF%25E0%25A5%2587%25E0%25A4%2582-.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EGorakhpur%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20December%2014%2C%2030-year-old%20Aarti%2C%20the%20wife%20of%20a%20migrant%20labourer%20trapped%20in%20a%20cycle%20of%20debt%20from%20micro-finance%20companies%2C%20took%20her%20life%20by%20consuming%20poison.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20agents%20of%20a%20micro-finance%20company%20which%20she%20had%20borrowed%20from%20had%20arrived%20at%20her%20and%20her%20relative%E2%80%99s%20houses.%20Humiliated%2C%20Aarti%20made%20a%20final%20phone%20call%20to%20her%20husband%2C%20noting%20that%20she%20was%20dying%20by%20suicide%20over%20her%20inability%20to%20pay%20the%20loans.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20at%20Mishrauli%20village%20of%20Sewrahi%20area%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Kushinagar%20district.%20The%20victim%E2%80%99s%20family%20members%20have%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20police%20against%20the%20micro-finance%20company%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20abetting%20the%20suicide.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20this%20incident%2C%20several%20cases%20of%20poor%20women%20in%20other%20villages%20like%20Mishrauli%20getting%20caught%20in%20a%20debt%20trap%20set%20by%20micro-finance%20companies%20have%20surfaced.%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20women%20mortgage%20their%20jewellery%20and%20land%20to%20repay%20the%20loan.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20also%20come%20to%20light%20that%20the%20agents%20of%20such%20micro-finance%20companies%20resort%20to%20harassment%20tactics%20to%20recover%20the%20loan%20and%20violate%20the%20guidelines%20issued%20by%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20routinely.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%2C%20there%20is%20a%20distressing%20pattern%20of%20the%20same%20person%20taking%20loans%20from%20several%20micro-finance%20companies%20at%20high%20interest%20rates.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Aarti%2C%20f%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eive%20micro-finance%20companies%20had%20given%20loans%20to%20her%20for%20agricultural%20work%20and%20to%20purchase%20cattle.%20Aarti%20used%20the%20loan%20amount%20towards%20the%20construction%20of%20her%20house%20for%20which%20the%20fund%20received%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana%20%E2%80%93%20less%20than%20Rs%201.20%20lakh%2C%20did%20not%20suffice.%20To%20repay%20the%20debt%20of%20owed%20to%20one%20company%2C%20she%20borrowed%20from%20another%20company%20and%20then%20from%20a%20third%20company%2C%20thus%20getting%20trapped%20in%20the%20cycle.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAarti%E2%80%99s%20husband%20Dharmanath%20Yadav%20works%20as%20a%20contract%20labourer%20in%20Najafgarh%20near%20Delhi.%20His%20job%20is%20to%20clean%20empty%20liquor%20bottles%20for%20which%20he%20gets%20paid%20Rs%2015%2C000%20to%20Rs%2016%2C000%20a%20month%20despite%20working%20four%20to%20five%20hours%20overtime%20each%20day.%20Most%20of%20these%20earnings%20had%20been%20going%20into%20the%20repayment%20of%20the%20loans.%20The%20family%20was%20in%20dire%20straits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21155701%2F%25E0%25A4%2586%25E0%25A4%25B0%25E0%25A4%25A4%25E0%25A5%2580-%25E0%