yment%20that%20day.%20Dharmnath%20had%20promised%20to%20send%20the%20money%20by%20afternoon%20but%20the%20agents%20of%20the%20micro-finance%20company%20reached%20Aarti%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%20the%20morning%20itself.%20Some%20other%20agents%20also%20reached%20Aarti%E2%80%99s%20maternal%20home%20in%20Beniya%20village%20to%20pressurise%20her%20further.%20Aarti%20eventually%20left%20her%20children%20at%20home%20and%20consumed%20poison%20at%20Brahmasthan%20in%20Sewrahi.%20Then%2C%20in%20a%20phone%20call%20to%20her%20husband%2C%20she%20told%20him%20that%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20repay%20the%20loans%20and%20requested%20him%20to%20take%20care%20of%20their%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20asked%20her%20why%20she%20took%20the%20step%20even%20though%20I%20was%20arranging%20for%20the%20money.%20She%20did%20not%20believe%20that%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%20arrange%20the%20amount.%20She%20also%20said%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20bear%20the%20humiliation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dharmanath%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20then%20switched%20off%20her%20phone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20called%20his%20mother-in-law%20Naina%20Devi.%20Thus%20alerted%2C%20Aarti%E2%80%99s%20parents%20found%20her%20and%20rushed%20her%20to%20the%20Banrha%20Community%20Health%20Centre%20and%20then%20to%20the%20District%20Hospital%20for%20treatment.%20She%20passed%20away%20that%20night%20itself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDharmanath%20only%20had%20Rs%20100%2C%20so%20he%20borrowed%20Rs%20500%20from%20a%20fellow%20labourer%20and%20boarded%20the%20train%20home.%20By%20the%20time%20he%20reached%20Mishrauli%20the%20next%20day%2C%20his%20wife%20had%20already%20died.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAarti%20and%20Dharmanath%20were%20married%20in%202014%20and%20have%20three%20children.%20The%20eldest%20son%20is%20seven%20years%20old%2C%20while%20two%20younger%20daughters%20are%20four%20and%20two%20years%20old.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDharmanath%20and%20his%20family%20had%20been%20displaced%20by%20river%20erosion%20in%202013.%20Earlier%2C%20he%20lived%20with%20his%20four%20brothers%20and%20parents%20in%20a%20tiny%20hut%20in%20a%20village%20named%20Nanhu%20Tola%2C%20located%20between%20the%20Narayani%20river%20and%20the%20embankment%20in%20Pipraghat.%20He%20also%20had%20agricultural%20land%20there.%20About%2060%20other%20families%20also%20lived%20in%20the%20village%20besides%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fembed%3Fpb%3D!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3572.7194846028883!2d86.25093165!3d26.43252755!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x39ec2a712a32c45b%253A0x8a61c95effa8de8f!2sPipra%2520Ghat%252C%2520Bihar!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1703152025130!5m2!1sen!2sin%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%20In%202013%2C%20four%20hamlets%20including%20Nanhu%20Tola%2C%20Phal%20Tola%2C%20Local%20Tola%20and%20Govardhan%20Tola%20were%20completely%20destroyed%20due%20to%20erosion%20by%20the%20Narayani%20river%20and%20houses%20and%20agricultural%20land%20were%20submerged.%20The%20government%20said%20it%20would%20settle%20the%20people%20displaced%20due%20to%20river%20erosion%20but%20no%20help%20was%20extended%20by%20the%20administration%20eventually%20and%20the%20displaced%20people%20settled%20wherever%20they%20could.%20Dharmanath%20and%20his%20brothers%20came%20to%20Mishrauli.%20Dharmanath%E2%80%99s%20father%20Brahma%20Yadav%20bought%20about%20four%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekattas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20a%20tract%20of%20severely%20uneven%20land.%20The%20family%20erected%20a%20hut%20and%20started%20living%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fover-1-lakh-houses-under-pmay-g-diverted-to-up-after-24-states-and-uts-fail-to-sanction-them%5C%22%3EOver%201%20Lakh%20Houses%20Under%20PMAY-G%20Diverted%20to%20UP%20After%2024%20States%20and%20UTs%20Fail%20to%20Sanction%20Them%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20youth%20of%20these%20families%20were%20forced%20to%20migrate%20to%20find%20work.%20Dharmanath%20and%20his%20three%20brothers%20also%20went%20to%20Delhi%20to%20work%20as%20labourers.%20Their%20earnings%20bought%20them%20their%20daily%20meals%20but%20the%20family%20was%20forced%20to%20continue%20living%20in%20the%20hut%2C%20they%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20four%20of%20the%20brothers%20applied%20for%20housing%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%20ago.%20When%20Dharmanath%20received%20Rs%201.20%20lakh%20for%20the%20construction%2C%20he%20started%20building%20the%20house.%20Since%20the%20land%20was%20full%20of%20pits%2C%20he%20had%20to%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20on%20building%20a%20strong%20foundation.%20He%20said%20Rs%2065%2C000%20was%20spent%20only%20on%20soil%20to%20fill%20the%20pits%20while%20the%20remaining%20amount%20was%20used%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20walls.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20Aarti%20came%20in%20touch%20with%20a%20group%20of%20women%20linked%20to%20micro-finance%20companies.%20In%20the%20hope%20of%20completing%20the%20house%2C%20she%20initially%20borrowed%20Rs%2030%2C000.%20However%2C%20this%20loan%20was%20granted%20to%20her%20in%20the%20name%20of%20agricultural%20work.%20When%20money%20fell%20short%2C%20she%20borrowed%20loans%20from%20five%20micro-finance%20companies%20one%20by%20one%20%E2%80%93%20Chaitanya%20India%20Fin%20Credit%20Private%20Limited%2C%20Bharat%20Financial%20Inclusion%20Limited%2C%20Suryodaya%20Small%20Finance%20Bank%20Limited%2C%20IIFL%20Samasta%20Finance%20Limited%2C%20and%20Utkarsh%20Small%20Finance%20Bank%20Limited.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuryoday%20Small%20Finance%20Bank%20Limited%20issued%20Aarti%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2028%2C000%20on%20February%2016%2C%202021%20for%20buying%20a%20buffalo.%20This%20loan%20was%20given%20at%2014%25%20flat%20interest%20which%20was%20to%20be%20repaid%20in%2024%20instalments%20of%20Rs%201%2C500%20each%20on%20May%203%2C%202023.%20Regarding%20this%20loan%2C%20documents%20recovered%20from%20Aarti%E2%80%99s%20house%20reveal%20information%20about%20payment%20of%20instalments%20till%20September%202022.%20Dharmanath%20could%20not%20provide%20information%20about%20whether%20other%20instalments%20were%20paid%20or%20whether%20Aarti%20was%20unable%20to%20pay%20them.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20document%20shows%20that%20Aarti%20was%20given%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20by%20Suryoday%20Small%20Finance%20Bank%20Limited%20on%20September%208%2C%202022%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%E2%80%98Agri%20AH%20Cow%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20was%20to%20be%20repaid%20in%2024%20instalments%20of%20Rs%202%2C700.%20Aarti%20had%20deposited%20one%20of%20the%20instalments%20on%20December%206.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIIFL%20Samasta%20Finance%20Limited%20gave%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20to%20Aarti%20for%20agricultural%20work%20at%20an%20effective%20interest%20rate%20of%2028.25%25%2C%20the%20instalment%20of%20which%20was%20Rs%201%2C220%20%E2%80%93%20to%20be%20paid%20on%20December%2014%2C%20the%20day%20Aarti%20died%20by%20suicide.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20Utkarsh%20Small%20Finance%20Bank%20Limited%20gave%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2030%2C000%20to%20her%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Agri%20Input%20at%2026.88%25%20annual%20interest%20on%20August%203%2C%202022%2C%20which%20was%20to%20be%20given%20in%2052%20instalments%20of%20Rs%20730%20each.%20Aarti%20had%20deposited%20one%20of%20its%20instalments%20on%20December%206%20and%20she%20was%20supposed%20to%20deposit%20its%2035th%20instalment%20on%20December%2020.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBharat%20Financial%20Inclusion%20Limited%20had%20given%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2030%2C000%20to%20Aarti%20on%20January%2019%2C%202023%2C%20with%20Rs%20500%20weekly%20instalments.%20Aarti%20could%20not%20pay%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EDecember%207%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20instalment%20of%20the%20loan.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20she%20had%20to%20pay%20Rs%201%2C000%20for%20this%20loan%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EDecember%2014%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAarti%20was%20also%20given%20a%20loan%20by%20Chaitanya%20India%20Fin%20Credit%20Private%20Limited.%20Dharmanath%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20exact%20loan%20amount.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20micro-finance%20companies%20also%20charged%20processing%20fees%20and%20other%20upfront%20charges%20ranging%20from%20Rs%20500%20to%20Rs%201%2C400%20while%20issuing%20the%20loans.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAarti%E2%80%99s%20three%20sisters-in-law%20said%20they%20had%20also%20borrowed%20loans%20from%20such%20micro-finance%20companies.%20Meena%20also%20invested%20the%20loan%20amount%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20house%20in%20anticipation%20of%20receiving%20funds%20under%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20housing%20scheme.%20But%20she%20got%20neither%20housing%20nor%20any%20funds%2C%20and%20today%20she%20has%20accumulated%20a%20debt%20of%20nearly%20Rs%202%20lakh%20for%20which%20she%20has%20to%20pay%20instalments%20of%20Rs%206%2C700%20every%20month.%20Meena%20said%20that%20they%20are%20so%20entangled%20in%20debt%20that%20they%20are%20forced%20to%20survive%20on%20the%20bare%20minimum.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20thought%20that%20we%20would%20at%20least%20be%20able%20to%20build%20the%20house%20but%20that%20too%20could%20not%20happen%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Meena.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21160343%2F%25E0%25A4%25AE%25E0%25A5%2580%25E0%25A4%25A8%25E0%25A4%25BE-.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21160343%2F%25E0%25A4%25AE%25E0%25A5%2580%25E0%25A4%25A8%25E0%25A4%25BE-.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21160343%2F%25E0%25A4%25AE%25E0%25A5%2580%25E0%25A4%25A8%25E0%25A4%25BE--300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21160343%2F%25E0%25A4%25AE%25E0%25A5%2580%25E0%25A4%25A8%25E0%25A4%25BE--1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-690185%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMeena.%20Photo%3A%20Manoj%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhere%20will%20we%20get%20the%20money%20to%20install%20the%20lintel%3F%20Right%20now%20our%20only%20worry%20is%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20debt.%20We%20will%20never%20get%20into%20it%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeena%20said%20that%20her%20sister-in-law%2C%20Aarti%2C%20was%20very%20worried%20about%20debt.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20all%20she%20could%20ever%20think%20of.%20She%20was%20even%20unable%20to%20eat%20properly.%20She%20was%20always%20anxious%20about%20the%20instalments.%20How%20much%20can%20a%20woman%20bear%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeena%E2%80%99s%20husband%20Jagarnath%20Yadav%20also%20works%20as%20a%20labourer%20in%20Delhi.%20Meena%20has%20four%20daughters.%20They%20have%20no%20other%20source%20of%20earning.%20Sometimes%20they%20manage%20to%20grow%20wheat%20in%20their%20submerged%20land.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20family%20was%20mired%20in%20debt%20ever%20since%20they%20were%20displaced%20after%20their%20agricultural%20land%20was%20destroyed%20by%20the%20river.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDharmanath%E2%80%99s%20younger%20brother%20Sheshnath%20also%20undertook%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20house%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20availing%20himself%20of%20funds%20under%20the%20PM%20housing%20scheme%20but%20is%20now%20in%20debt.%20He%20said%20that%20his%20plot%20of%20land%20has%20%E2%80%9Ceight-foot%20deep%20pits.%E2%80%9D%20To%20fill%20it%2C%20he%20had%20to%20spend%20Rs%2065%2C000%20on%20130%20trolleys%20of%20soil.%20It%20took%20five%20quintals%20of%20rebar%20and%20four%20trolley%20bricks%20to%20lay%20the%20foundation.%20In%20addition%2C%20it%20costs%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20to%20Rs%203%20lakh%20to%20prepare%20the%20foundation%20alone.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20wife%20Rajal%20Devi%20borrowed%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20for%20this%20purpose%20from%20micro-finance%20companies.%20At%20present%2C%20he%20is%20paying%20Rs%2012%2C000%20per%20month%20as%20an%20instalment%20of%20this%20loan.%20Here%20too%2C%20their%20entire%20income%20is%20spent%20on%20repaying%20this%20loan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDharmanath%E2%80%99s%20elder%20brother%20Baijnath%20also%20works%20as%20a%20labourer%20in%20Delhi.%20His%20wife%20Gudiya%20has%20also%20taken%20loans%20from%20micro-finance%20companies.%20She%20pays%20three%20instalments%20of%20Rs%201%2C230%2C%20Rs%201%2C100%20and%20Rs%201%2C270%20every%2015%20days%20and%20one%20instalment%20of%20Rs%203%2C210%20every%20month.%20He%20also%20used%20the%20loan%20amount%20to%20build%20a%20house%20but%20the%20house%20is%20still%20incomplete.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAcross%20the%20village%2C%20a%20familiar%20story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsha%20Devi%2C%20a%20Dalit%20resident%20of%20the%20village%2C%20had%20leased%20one%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebigha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20agricultural%20land%20so%20that%20she%20could%20manage%20her%20household%20expenses%20through%20farming.%20She%20borrowed%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20from%20a%20micro-finance%20company%20to%20arrange%20fertilizer%2C%20water%20and%20seeds.%20To%20pay%20the%20instalments%2C%20she%20borrowed%20another%20loan%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20each%20from%20two%20companies.%20Now%2C%20she%20is%20paying%20instalments%20of%20Rs%202%2C700%2C%20Rs%201%2C230%2C%20Rs%20805%2C%20Rs%202%2C030%20and%20Rs%202%2C100%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%206%2C765%20%E2%80%93%20every%20month%2C%20to%20repay%20the%20loans.%20She%20also%20had%20to%20give%20up%20the%20leased%20land.%20Her%20husband%20Virendra%20works%20in%20a%20scrap%20factory%20in%20Chandigarh.%20He%20had%20received%20money%20under%20the%20PM%20housing%20scheme.%20When%20the%20amount%20of%20Rs%201.2%20lakh%20from%20the%20government%20fell%20short%20in%20the%20construction%2C%20he%20invested%20the%20loan%20amount%20taken%20from%20the%20micro-finance%20company%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20local%20resident%20Guddi%E2%80%99s%20husband%20Sanjay%20Chauhan%20works%20as%20a%20labourer%20in%20Delhi.%20Guddi%20has%20availed%20four%20loans%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%2C%20Rs%2035%2C000%2C%20Rs%2045%2C000%20and%20Rs%2028%2C000%20from%20micro-finance%20companies%20for%20which%20she%20has%20to%20pay%20instalments%20of%20Rs%201%2C230%2C%20Rs%20860%2C%20Rs%202%2C410%20and%20Rs%20500%20respectively.%20Guddi%20had%20to%20pay%20an%20instalment%20of%20Rs%202%2C410%20on%20December%2014%20as%20well%20but%20she%20did%20not%20have%20the%20money.%20The%20micro-finance%20company%E2%80%99s%20agent%20started%20pressuring%20her%20to%20sell%20some%20household%20items%20to%20pay%20the%20instalment.%20When%20Guddi%20told%20him%20that%20she%20did%20not%20have%20any%20goods%20to%20sell%2C%20the%20agent%20forcibly%20seized%20her%20sewing%20machine%20worth%20Rs%205%2C000.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20news%20of%20Aarti%E2%80%99s%20death%20by%20suicide%20reached%20the%20village%2C%20the%20agent%20fled%20after%20leaving%20the%20sewing%20machine%20at%20Aarti%E2%80%99s%20house.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20group%20of%2032%20women%20in%20Mishrauli%20village%20are%20trapped%20in%20a%20web%20of%20debt%20from%20four%20to%20five%20micro-finance%20companies.%20The%20head%20of%20the%20group%2C%20Samintar%20Devi%2C%20took%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20to%20buy%20a%20buffalo%20and%20then%20another%20loan%20of%20Rs%2045%2C000.%20She%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98group%E2%80%99%20initially%20had%2010%20women%20but%20now%2032%20women%20are%20in%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20RBI%20guidelines%2C%20a%20creditor%20can%20neither%20threaten%20a%20borrower%20nor%20use%20abusive%20language%20to%20recover%20the%20loan.%20The%20creditor%20cannot%20call%20the%20borrower%20on%20the%20phone%20continuously%20and%20only%20call%20between%209%20am%20and%206%20pm.%20Also%2C%20relatives%2C%20friends%20and%20colleagues%20of%20the%20borrower%20cannot%20be%20harassed%20for%20loan%20recovery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fbig-talk-small-action-modi-govts-work-on-womens-empowerment-in-the-last-9-years%5C%22%3EBig%20Talk%2C%20Small%20Action%3A%20Modi%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20Work%20on%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Empowerment%20in%20the%20Last%209%20Years%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJewellery%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20women%20of%20Mishrauli%20village%20said%20that%20the%20agents%20of%20the%20micro-finance%20company%20come%20to%20their%20houses%20with%20six%20to%20seven%20people%20and%20stay%20there%20until%20they%20get%20the%20money.%20They%20even%20reach%20their%20relatives%E2%80%99%20houses%20and%20exert%20pressure%20to%20repay%20the%20loan%20amount%20by%20selling%20household%20items.%20After%20some%20instalments%20of%20the%20loan%20are%20paid%2C%20a%20new%20loan%20is%20issued.%20In%20this%20way%2C%20four%20to%20five%20micro-finance%20companies%20grant%20loans%20to%20women%20and%20get%20them%20entangled%20in%20a%20debt%20trap.%20The%20situation%20is%20such%20that%20more%20loans%20are%20being%20availed%20to%20repay%20the%20loans.%20They%20are%20also%20borrowing%20money%20from%20relatives%20and%20mortgaging%20jewellery%20and%20land.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20of%20the%20women%20caught%20in%20this%20debt%20trap%20of%20micro-finance%20companies%20have%20had%20to%20mortgage%20their%20jewellery.%20Sumitra%20and%20Rajpati%20said%20that%20they%20had%20mortgaged%20four%20pieces%20of%20jewellery%20each%20while%20Laichi%20paid%20her%20loan%20instalment%20by%20mortgaging%20two%20pieces%20of%20jewellery%20for%20Rs%2020%2C000.%20Guddi%20Devi%20has%20mortgaged%20her%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emangalsutra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20anklets.%20Asha%20Devi%20also%20claimed%20that%20five%20of%20her%20jewellery%20pieces%20have%20been%20mortgaged.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20not%20a%20single%20family%20here%20that%20has%20not%20mortgaged%20something%20or%20the%20other%20at%20the%20goldsmith%E2%80%99s%20shop.%20Once%20something%20is%20mortgaged%2C%20it%20is%20not%20even%20released%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAjay%20Kumar%20Lallu%2C%20former%20state%20president%20of%20Congress%20and%20MLA%20of%20Tamkuhiraj%2C%20posted%20on%20X%20regarding%20this%20incident.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECPI%20(ML)%20leader%20Paramhans%20Singh%2C%20along%20with%20two%20other%20organisations%2C%20have%20released%20a%20fact-finding%20report%20on%20the%20incident%20of%20Aarti%E2%80%99s%20death.%20Local%20leaders%20have%20demanded%20the%20registration%20of%20a%20case%20of%20murder%20against%20the%20micro-finance%20company%2C%20the%20waiving%20off%20of%20all%20the%20loans%20given%20by%20such%20companies%20to%20the%20poor%2C%20compensation%20of%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20to%20Aarti%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20and%20checking%20the%20licence%20of%20such%20companies%20as%20per%20RBI%20guidelines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20know%20someone%20%E2%80%93%20friend%20or%20family%20member%20%E2%80%93%20at%20risk%20of%20suicide%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20them.%20The%20Suicide%20Prevention%20India%20Foundation%20maintains%20a%20list%20of%20telephone%20numbers%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.spif.in%2Fseek-help%2F%5C%22%3Ewww.spif.in%2Fseek-help%2F%3C%2Fa%3E)%20they%20can%20call%20to%20speak%20in%20confidence.%20You%20could%20also%20refer%20them%20to%20the%20nearest%20hospital.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703158207000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21155111%2F%25E0%25A4%2595%25E0%25A4%25B0%25E0%25A5%258D%25E0%25A4%259C-%25E0%25A4%2595%25E0%25A5%2587-%25E0%25A4%25A6%25E0%25A4%25B8%25E0%25A5%258D%25E0%25A4%25A4%25E0%25A4%25BE%25E0%25A4%25B5%25E0%25A5%2587%25E0%25A4%259C%25E0%25A5%258B%25E0%25A4%2582-%25E0%25A4%2595%25E0%25A5%2587-%25E0%25A4%25B8%25E0%25A4%25BE%25E0%25A4%25A5-%25E0%25A4%25AE%25E0%25A4%25B9%25E0%25A4%25BF%25E0%25A4%25B2%25E0%25A4%25BE%25E0%25A4%25AF%25E0%25A5%2587%25E0%25A4%2582-.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Floan-debt-trap-micro-finance-companies%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Most%20residents%20of%20a%20village%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20live%20in%20mortal%20fear%20of%20the%20inability%20to%20pay%20back%20loans%20they%20have%20taken%20from%20micro-finance%20companies%20whose%20agents%20are%20not%20above%20threats%20and%20coercion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Floan-debt-trap-micro-finance-companies%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iraqi%20and%20Palestinian%20Projects%20Take%20Top%20Prizes%20in%20CineGouna%20Springboard%20Awards%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703158182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fcinegouna-springboa