rom%20the%20project's%20conceptualization.%20The%20%E2%80%98Yeh%20Jawaani%20Hai%20Deewani%E2%80%99%20star%20seamlessly%20fit%20into%20the%20character%20of%20Ranvijay.%20Ranbir%20Kapoor's%20filmography%20has%20showcased%20his%20versatility%2C%20exploring%20diverse%20genres%20from%20the%20innocent%20Mickey%20in%20%E2%80%98Tu%20Jhoothi%20Main%20Makkaar%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20intense%20roles%20in%20%E2%80%98Rockstar%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Sanju%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20now%20%E2%80%98Animal%E2%80%99.%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga%20lauded%20Kapoor's%20ability%20to%20portray%20a%20range%20of%20characters%20effectivel%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdirector-sandeep-reddy-vanga-clears-the-air-on-initial-casting-rumours-for-animal-ranbir-kapoor-was-the-first-choice-not-mahesh-babu%2Farticleshow%2F106183975.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20couple%20built%203%20luxury%20treehouses%20on%20a%20picturesque%20Welsh%20farm%20and%20now%20rent%20them%20out%20%E2%80%94%20see%20inside%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20smiling%20couple%20with%20sheep%20in%20the%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658040b4a79e5746976a6828%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELaura%20and%20John%20Lewis.%3Cp%3ERuth%20Rees%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELaura%20and%20John%20Lewis%2C%20a%20couple%20from%20Wales%2C%20built%20three%20luxury%20treehouses%20on%20their%20hillside%20farm.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20latest%20treehouse%2C%20over%20a%20stream%2C%20cost%20the%20couple%20%C2%A3150%2C000%20and%20took%20six%20months%20to%20build.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThey%20now%20rent%20the%20treehouses%20out%20in%20addition%20to%20working%20on%20their%20farm.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20spring%202017%2C%20the%20Welsh%20sheep%20farmers%20Laura%20and%20John%20Lewis%20knew%20they%20needed%20another%20income%20to%20make%20their%20hillside%20farm%20more%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Lewis%2C%20a%20trained%20carpenter%20whose%20family%20has%20owned%20the%20farm%20for%20three%20generations%2C%20wanted%20to%20build%20something%20on%20the%20land.%20At%20first%2C%20the%20couple%20thought%20they%20might%20build%20a%20holiday%20lodge.%20He%20trawled%20holiday-booking%20sites%20to%20see%20which%20homes%20jumped%20off%20the%20page.%20He%20decided%20instead%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20farm%20loan%2C%20to%20build%20a%20treehouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20built%20oak-framed%20houses%2C%20but%20this%20would%20be%20his%20first%20treehouse.%20The%20couple%20chose%20a%20large%20oak%20tree%20in%20a%20secluded%20part%20of%20the%20farm%20so%20their%20future%20guests%20would%20have%20some%20privacy.%20Then%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20local%20architect%2C%20they%20drew%20up%20the%20plans%20for%20the%20treehouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20they%20were%20going%20to%20create%20an%20off-the-grid%20eco-hideaway%2C%20but%20then%20Laura%20Lewis%20said%20she%20knew%20she%20couldn't%20do%20without%20modern%20conveniences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20feel%20very%20comfortable%20building%20something%20I%20wouldn't%20stay%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20So%20they%20started%20to%20design%20a%20luxury%20treehouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221620%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20a%20multiroom%20treehouse%20on%20a%20wooden%20frame%20with%20a%20balcony%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65804176a79e5746976a6847%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20second%20treehouse%20the%20Lewises%20built.%3Cp%3EToWander%20UK%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20luxury%20treehouse%20was%20immediately%20more%20challenging.%20Their%20application%20for%20planning%20permission%20%E2%80%94%20formal%20approval%20from%20the%20authorities%20required%20for%20construction%20in%20the%20UK%20%E2%80%94%20was%20slow.%20Then%20the%20farm%20was%20struck%20by%20a%20snowstorm%2C%20which%20meant%20they%20were%20cut%20off%20from%20the%20site%20for%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20snow%20disappeared%20after%20four%20weeks%2C%20but%20the%20ground%20was%20so%20wet%20we%20couldn't%20carry%20any%20materials%20to%20the%20site%2C%26quot%3B%20Laura%20Lewis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20his%20father%2C%20John%20Lewis%20then%20started%20building%20the%20treehouse%2C%20which%20they%20called%20Trawscwm.%20The%20treehouse%20and%20its%20shingle%20roof%20were%20made%20with%20locally%20sourced%20oak%2C%20larch%2C%20and%20red%20cedar%2C%20as%20well%20as%20pieces%20of%20wood%20they%20retrieved%20from%20the%20farm.%20The%20ground%20floor%20featured%20a%20living%20space%2C%20bedroom%2C%20and%20bathroom.%20It%20also%20had%20a%20ladder%20to%20take%20guests%20to%20the%20loft%2C%20where%20another%20bed%20was%20tucked%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Interior%20shot%20of%20a%20tree%20house%20with%20mounted%20TV%2C%20couch%20and%20chair%20and%20stairs%20leading%20up%20to%20bedroom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65803693a79e5746976a6697%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20interior%20of%20Trawscwm.%3Cp%3EToWander%20UK%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20the%20treehouse%20could%20get%20electricity%20and%20water%2C%20they%20had%20to%20dig%20a%20borehole%20and%20pay%20a%20one-off%20fee%20for%20it%20to%20be%20connected%20to%20the%20electricity%20mains.%20Laura%20Lewis%20said%20plumbers%20and%20electricians%20were%20scarce%20and%20in%20demand%20in%20their%20rural%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20spent%20%C2%A3100%2C000%2C%20or%20about%20%24126%2C000%2C%20to%20build%20Trawscwm.%20It%20opened%20in%20June%202018.%20At%20first%2C%20they%20worried%20such%20a%20rural%20location%20would%20struggle%20to%20get%20guests.%20But%20when%20they%20launched%20the%20treehouse%20on%20the%20glamping%20website%20Canopy%20%26amp%3B%20Stars%2C%20it%20was%20soon%20booked%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20have%20a%20day%20empty%20for%20about%20six%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Laura%20Lewis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20originally%20planned%20to%20build%20only%20one%20treehouse%2C%20the%20speed%20at%20which%20bookings%20came%20in%20encouraged%20them%20to%20build%20another.%20The%20couple%20chose%20a%20site%20in%20the%20field%20next%20to%20the%20first%20treehouse%2C%20in%20a%20tree%20with%20views%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FRadnor_Forest%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERadnor%20Forest%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20treehouse%20was%20quite%20secluded%2C%20whereas%20this%20one%20would%20be%20all%20about%20the%20views%2C%26quot%3B%20Laura%20Lewis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20looked%20at%20the%20images%20guests%20tagged%20the%20treehouse%20in%20on%20Instagram%20to%20see%20what%20they%20liked%20about%20it%2C%20such%20as%20a%20countryside%20view%20from%20the%20bathtub.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20liked%20the%20'wow'%20features%2C%20so%20we%20thought%20about%20this%20for%20the%20next%20design%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221620%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20living%20room%20in%20a%20treehouse%20with%20a%20view%20across%20a%20forest%20in%20the%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6580385250edbc52a8652600%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20from%20the%20Cadwollen%20treehouse%3Cp%3EToWander%20UK%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Trawscwm%2C%20the%20Cadwollen%20treehouse%20included%20a%20copper%20tub.%20It%20also%20had%20a%20suspended%20hammock%20on%20the%20second%20floor%20above%20the%20lounge%20and%20a%20hot%20tub%20on%20a%20pier%20jutting%20out%20from%20the%20deck%2C%208%20meters%20above%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Lewis%20brought%20in%20extra%20workers%20and%20machinery%20to%20help%20fulfill%20their%20plans%20for%20an%20extended%20deck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20concerned%20about%20the%20wind%2C%20but%20we%20made%20sure%20it%20was%20extremely%20strong%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20him%20and%20his%20dad%20nine%20months%20to%20build%20the%20next%20treehouse.%20In%202019%2C%20they%20launched%20it%20on%20Canopy%20%26amp%3B%20Stars%20but%20noticed%20that%20their%20treehouses%20were%20attracting%20bookings%20via%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstagram%20was%20becoming%20a%20massive%20income%20stream%2C%26quot%3B%20Laura%20Lewis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202020%2C%20the%20couple%20created%20a%20website%2C%20called%20ToWander%20UK%2C%20to%20showcase%20their%20treehouses%20and%20holiday%20homes%20on%20other%20farms.%20While%20they%20didn't%20charge%20anyone%20for%20listings%20early%20in%20the%20pandemic%2C%20they%20now%20charge%20members%20%C2%A3250%20to%20%C2%A3475%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20the%20two%20treehouses%20and%20the%20website%20became%20so%20successful%20that%20Laura%20Lewis%20left%20her%20role%20in%20education%20to%20look%20after%20their%20booking%20site.%20They%20could%20afford%20to%20pay%20her%20a%20salary%2C%20as%20they%20were%20no%20longer%20paying%20a%2020%25%20commission%20to%20Canopy%20%26amp%3B%20Stars%20for%20bookings%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cement%20truck%20delivers%20cement%20to%20a%20construction%20site%20in%20a%20field%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6581b698a79e5746976ae47a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20truck%20delivered%20cement%20to%20the%20construction%20site%20of%20the%20third%20treehouse.%3Cp%3EToWander%20UK%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20treehouse%20was%20their%20most%20challenging.%20Designed%20for%20families%2C%20it%20sleeps%20seven%20and%20wraps%20around%20five%20trees.%20They%20also%20chose%20to%20build%20it%20over%20a%20stream%20and%20add%20a%20slide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20received%20planning%20permission%20to%20build%20it%2C%20they%20were%20about%20to%20start%20work%20in%20March%202020%20but%20had%20to%20stop%20when%20the%20country%20went%20into%20lockdown.%20A%20month%20later%2C%20John%20Lewis'%20father%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20were%20now%20building%20during%20a%20pandemic%2C%20they%20were%20beset%20with%20delays.%20Wood%20was%20in%20short%20supply%20and%20expensive.%20Because%20they%20had%20chosen%20the%20banks%20of%20a%20stream%20to%20build%20on%2C%20the%20ground%20was%20wet%2C%20so%20they%20decided%20to%20use%20a%20steel%20frame.%20A%20truck%20had%20to%20navigate%20the%20muddy%20field%20to%20pour%20the%20concrete%20for%20the%20frame's%20footings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20frame%20came%20to%20the%20site%20in%20individual%20lengths%2C%20and%20then%20we%20bolted%20it%20together%20on%20the%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20Lewis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20complete%2C%20they%20used%20a%20crane%20to%20lift%20the%20steel%20frame%20into%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20house%20on%20a%20steel%20frame%20under%20construction%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658033e11c5c7b8c9a09297f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20third%20treehouse%20under%20construction.%3Cp%3EToWander%20UK%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20finished%20it%20in%20December%202020.%20The%20build%20cost%20%C2%A3150%2C000.%20But%20as%20they%20were%20about%20to%20open%20for%20Christmas%2C%20the%20country%20went%20into%20lockdown%20again.%20The%20treehouses%20remained%20empty%20for%20the%20next%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20furnished%20the%20treehouses%2C%20they%20used%20some%20products%20from%20the%20furniture%20store%20Dunelm%2C%20which%20Laura%20Lewis%20tagged%20in%20the%20images%20on%20Instagram.%20The%20Dunelm%20team%20reached%20out%20to%20her%20to%20ask%20if%20it%20could%20use%20one%20of%20them.%20It%20then%20suggested%20a%20competition%20for%20a%20stay%20in%20a%20treehouse.%20When%20the%20competition%20went%20live%20in%20November%202020%2C%20Laura%20Lewis%20said%20their%20Instagram%20account%20grew%20by%20about%2044%2C000%20followers%20in%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20a%20couple%20asked%20if%20they%20could%20renew%20their%20vows%20in%20one%20of%20the%20treehouses.%20The%20Lewises%20didn't%20need%20to%20be%20licensed%20to%20hold%20the%20blessing%2C%20but%20they%20applied%20for%20a%20venue%20marriage%20license%20to%20conduct%20weddings%20there.%20In%202022%2C%20they%20held%2018%20weddings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20still%20work%209-to-5%20in%20an%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20Laura%20Lewis%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20that%20John%20might%20have%20to%20also%20drive%20between%20the%20treehouses%20on%20a%20quad%20bike%20with%20clean%20bed%20linen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20also%20busy%20with%20their%20farm%2C%20and%20when%20it's%20lambing%20season%2C%20the%20guests%20can%20visit%20the%20lambing%20shed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaura%20and%20John%20Lewis%20also%20now%20have%20a%20team%20to%20help%20with%20their%20treehouses%20and%20the%20ToWander%20UK%20website.%20They%20have%20three%20part-time%20cleaners%20and%20three%20part-time%20staff%20members%20who%20oversee%20social%20media%2C%20admin%2C%20and%20finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20are%20now%20planning%20their%20fourth%20treehouse%2C%20aimed%20at%20couples%2C%20which%20they%20hope%20to%20build%20next%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-this-couple-built-luxury-treehouses-on-welsh-farm-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703157942000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658040bd50edbc52a8652727%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-this-couple-built-luxury-treehouses-on-welsh-farm-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Linda%20and%20John%20Lewis%20built%20three%20luxury%20treehouses%20on%20their%20farm.%20They%20initially%20rented%20them%20out%20via%20a%20glamping%20website%20but%20later%20launched%20their%20own%20website.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Claire%20Turrell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-this-couple-built-luxury-treehouses-on-welsh-farm-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Salaar'%20VS%20'Dunki'%3A%20Rift%20regarding%20screens%20finally%20ends%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703157490000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106183633%2Cimgsize-62688.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsalaar-vs-dunki-rift-regarding-screens-finally-ends-prabhas-starrer-to-release-in-national-chains-with-equal-sharing-with-shah-rukh-khans-film%2Farticleshow%2F106183519.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20the%20last%20few%20days%2C%20there%20was%20a%20huge%20rift%20going%20on%20as%20two%20biggies%20'Salaar%20Part%201%3A%20Ceasefire'%20and%20'Dunki'%20clash%20at%20the%20box%20office.%20Reportedly%2C%20some%20theatre%20chains%20were%20not%20being%20fair%20by%20giving%20equal%20number%20of%20screens%20to%20the%20Prabhas%20starrer.%20However%2C%20the%20issue%2