emark%20was%20about%20wrestlers%20who%20had%20protested%20against%20and%20accused%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20for%20several%20months.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20triumph%20for%20the%20thousands%20of%20wrestlers%20in%20the%20country%20who%20suffered%20in%20the%20past%207-8%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sanjay%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPTI_News%2Fstatus%2F1737776240851853441%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%E2%80%99s%20panel%2C%20which%20was%20backed%20by%20the%20former%20WFI%20president%2C%20defeated%20the%20panel%20led%20by%20Commonwealth%20Games%20gold%20medallist%20Anita%20Sheoran.%20Sheoran%E2%80%99s%20panel%20received%20support%20from%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20top%20wrestlers%20who%20had%20accused%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20fraternity%20knows%20who%20has%20worked%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20the%20sports%20and%20who%20has%20tried%20to%20cause%20damage.%20The%20work%20done%20by%20the%20WFI%20in%20the%20last%2011%20years%20is%20proof%20that%20the%20sport%20of%20wrestling%20has%20grown%20at%20a%20good%20pace%20in%20India.%20People%20will%20have%20that%20in%20mind%20when%20they%20will%20cast%20their%20votes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sanjay%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fsports%2Fbrij-bhushan-sharan-singhs-loyalist-sanjay-singh-confident-of-getting-wfi-top-job-2819284%5C%22%3Ehad%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESakshi%20Malik%2C%20an%20Olympic%20medallist%20who%20was%20one%20of%20the%20faces%20of%20the%20protest%20against%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20said%20she%20would%20quit%20wrestling.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20gathered%20a%20lot%20of%20courage%20for%20this%20fight%20against%20the%20WFI%20President%20(Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh).%20But%20today%2C%20his%20right%20hand%20(referring%20to%20Sanjay%20Si