appointment%20of%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioners%20and%20Election%20Commissioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20had%20approved%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20Other%20Election%20Commissioners%20(Appointment%2C%20Conditions%20of%20Service%20and%20Term%20of%20Office)%20Bill%2C%202023.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20legislation%20has%20now%20cleared%20parliament.%20It%20will%20now%20go%20to%20the%20President%20for%20her%20assent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20legislation%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%2C%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20said%20the%201991%20Act%20on%20the%20service%20conditions%20of%20top%20poll%20officers%20was%20a%20half-baked%20attempt%20and%20the%20present%20Bill%20covers%20the%20areas%20left%20out%20by%20the%20previous%20legislation.%20The%20Bill%20was%20then%20passed%20by%20a%20voice%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20underwent%20substantial%20changes%20following%20objections%20from%20various%20quarters.%C2%A0The%20Opposition%20has%20slammed%20the%20legislation%2C%20saying%20it%20would%20compromise%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20poll%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20that%20election%20commissioners%20must%20be%20appointed%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20a%20panel%20comprising%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20and%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India.%20The%20landmark%20judgment%20was%20aimed%20at%20insulating%20the%20top%20election%20body%20from%20political%20interference.%20The%20court%2C%20however%2C%20held%20that%20the%20judgment%20will%20hold%20good%20till%20government%20comes%20up%20with%20a%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20new%20legislation%2C%20the%20government%20replaced%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20with%20a%20Union%20Minister.%20This%2C%20the%20Opposition%20has%20alleged%2C%20gives%20the%20government%20greater%20powers%20on%20the%20appointment%20of%20top%20poll%20officers%20and%20compromises%20the%20autonomy%20of%20the%20poll%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20discussion%20the%20Bill%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Randeep%20Surjewala%20said%20the%20autonomy%2C%20fearlessness%20and%20fairness%20of%20India's%20democracy%20and%20electoral%20machinery%20have%20been%20crushed%20by%20a%20bulldozer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi%20government%20has%20attacked%20the%20democracy%20of%20India.%20The%20autonomy%2C%20fearlessness%20and%20fairness%20of%20India's%20democracy%20and%20electoral%20machinery%20have%20been%20crushed%20by%20a%20bulldozer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20point%20in%20the%20Bill%20that%20had%20drawn%20protests%20from%20former%20poll%20officers%20was%20a%20proposal%20to%20strip%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20other%20Election%20Commissioners%20of%20the%20status%20of%20Supreme%20Court%20judges%2C%20and%20bring%20their%20salary%20and%20rank%20on%20par%20with%20an%20officer%20of%20Cabinet%20Secretary-rank.%20The%20government%20later%20decided%20to%20undo%20this%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703153640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2F51qsbfd_election-commission-reuters_625x300_05_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbill-to-appoint-top-3-election-commissioners-passed-in-lok-sabha-4715210%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20most%20Opposition%20members%20outside%20the%20House%20after%20a%20spree%20of%20suspensions%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20passed%20a%20Bill%20to%20establish%20a%20new%20mechanism%20for%20appointment%20of%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioners%20and%20Election%20Commissioners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbill-to-appoint-top-3-election-commissioners-passed-in-lok-sabha-4715210%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F