39886068-3975.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fhc-asks-centre-to-consider-representation-for-linking-property-with-aadhaar-123122100495_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20said%20the%20representation%20shall%20be%20decided%20by%20the%20government%20within%20three%20months%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fhc-asks-centre-to-consider-representation-for-linking-property-with-aadhaar-123122100495_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Dunki%20Is%20Buoyed%20By%20Flawless%20Performances%20From%20SRK%2C%20Taapsee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20principal%20strength%20of%20%3Ci%3EDunki%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20directed%20and%20edited%20by%20Rajkumar%20Hirani%2C%20springboards%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20does%20not%20rely%20solely%20on%20Shahrukh%20Khan's%20phenomenal%20star%20power.%20There%20can%20be%20no%20denying%20that%20without%20the%20lead%20actor's%20singular%20charisma%20this%20would%20not%20be%20the%20film%20that%20it%20is.%20But%20its%20charm%20stems%20equally%20from%20a%20slam-dunk%20solid%20screenplay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EDunki%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20written%20by%20Hirani%2C%20Abhijat%20Joshi%20and%20Kanika%20Dhillon%2C%20deals%20with%20the%20perils%20of%20illegal%20immigration%20with%20infectious%20jollity%2C%20piercing%20drama%20and%20a%20clear-eyed%20awareness%20of%20the%20ethical%20and%20legal%20questions%20surrounding%20the%20act%20of%20entering%20a%20foreign%20country%20without%20a%20visa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20circularity%20of%20the%20story%20evokes%20all%20the%20confusions%20that%20stalk%20the%20prodigals%20as%20they%20dangle%20between%20their%20aspirations%20and%20the%20realities%20of%20the%20path%20they%20have%20chosen.%20It%20is%20at%20the%20same%20time%20informed%20with%20near-perfect%20structural%20roundness%20as%20it%20examines%20the%20fears%20and%20misgivings%20of%20those%20who%20deign%20to%20flee%20their%20land%20and%20seek%20a%20new%20life%20surrounded%20by%20strangers%20in%20a%20faraway%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20half%20of%20%3Ci%3EDunki%3C%2Fi%3E%20-%20the%20film%20kicks%20off%20with%20an%20old%20woman%20giving%20a%20London%20hospital%20the%20slip%20and%20landing%20up%20in%20an%20immigration%20advocate's%20office%20with%20a%20plea%20for%20help%20-%20is%20consistently%20lively%20and%20frequently%20funny.%20The%20second%20segment%20of%20the%2016o-minute%20film%20anchors%20itself%20in%20a%20more%20solemn%20tone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20dangerous%20voyage%20without%20maps%20across%20a%20river%2C%20a%20desert%2C%20a%20snow-covered%20mountain%20and%20a%20wilderness%20that%20extends%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20horizon%20brings%20death%20and%20disaster%20in%20its%20wake.%20All%20this%20transpires%20after%20the%20hero%20and%20his%20mates%20have%20tried%20every%20trick%20in%20the%20book%20to%20hoodwink%20their%20way%20through%20the%20IELTS%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EDunki%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20buoyed%20by%20an%20array%20of%20flawless%20performances%2C%20with%20the%20lead%20actor%20and%20Taapsee%20Pannu%2C%20playing%20a%20woman%20who%20is%20far%20more%20than%20just%20the%20hero's%20romantic%20interest%2C%20leading%20the%20way%20through%20the%20ups%20and%20downs%20-%20more%20of%20the%20latter%20really%20-%20triggered%20by%20the%20characters'%20repeated%20leaps%20of%20faith%20across%20unknown%20terrains%20and%20into%20an%20equally%20alien%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20core%20of%20the%20plot%20is%20a%20love%20story%20that%20springs%20many%20a%20surprise.%20But%20in%20doing%20so%20it%20does%20not%20have%20to%20labour%20overly%20hard.%20It%20strikes%20a%20neat%20balance%20between%20heart%2C%20head%20and%20soul%2C%20crafting%20an%20emotionally%20engaging%20tale%20with%20its%20fair%20share%20of%20twists%20that%20do%20not%20strain%20credulity%20beyond%20reasonable%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EDunki%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20co-produced%20by%20Red%20Chillies%20Entertainment%2C%20carves%20out%20distinct%20(if%20not%20equal%20in%20terms%20of%20screen%20time)%20spaces%20for%20the%20four%20pivotal%20characters%20-%20a%20never-say-die%20ex-soldier%20Hardayal%20%26quot%3BHardy%26quot%3B%20Dhillon%20(SRK)%2C%20Manu%20Randhawa%20(Taapsee%20Pannu)%2C%20Buggu%20Lakhanpal%20(Vikram%20Kochhar)%20and%20Balli%20Kakkar%20(Anil%20Grover).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20them%20has%20a%20story%2C%20and%20every%20story%20counts%20for%20more%20than%20the%20footage%20that%20is%20accorded%20to%20it%20because%20all%20of%20them%20contribute%20substantially%20to%20the%20tapestry%20of%20experiences%20and%20impulses%20that%20constitutes%20the%20storyline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuggu's%20mother%20works%20as%20a%20security%20guard%20in%20a%20factory%20to%20keep%20the%20home%20fires%20burning.%20Balli's%20mom%20does%20odd%20tailoring%20jobs%20to%20feed%20the%20family.%20And%20Manu%20has%20had%20her%20home%20taken%20away%20from%20her%20as%20a%20result%20of%20an%20unrepaid%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20moves%20between%20the%20present%20and%20the%20mid-1990s%20and%20revolves%20around%20a%20trio%20of%20young%20and%20restless%20residents%20of%20Laltu%2C%20Punjab.%20Manu%2C%20Buggu%20and%20Balli%20dream%20of%20winging%20it%20to%20London%20no%20matter%20what.%20They%20are%20determined%20to%20get%20away%20from%20the%20poverty%20that%20they%20are%20trapped%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20three%20has%20to%20literally%20break%20the%20bank%20to%20fund%20his%20aspiration%2C%20another%20has%20to%20learn%20the%20rudiments%20of%20wrestling%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20visa%20in%20the%20sports%20category%20and%20all%20of%20them%20have%20to%20enrol%20in%20a%20spoken%20English%20academy%20run%20by%20Geetu%20Gulati%20(Boman%20Irani)%2C%20who%20claims%20that%20a%20passage%20to%20England%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20piece%20of%20cake%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20attempts%20backfire%20pretty%20badly.%20A%20couple%20of%20lives%20are%20lost%2C%20money%20is%20squandered%20and%20moves%20learnt%20in%20a%20wrestling%20pit%20come%20to%20naught%20when%20it%20really%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FACKQDAlAfFE%3Fsi%3DpNlCNeCc9PiB1IDP%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFortunately%20for%20the%20three%20drifters%2C%20an%20exceptionally%20enterprising%20Hardy%20Dhillon%20of%20Pathankot%20lands%20in%20their%20midst%20with%20a%20specific%20personal%20purpose%20and%20then%20proceeds%20to%20become%20their%20go-to%20man%20for%20everything%20except%20English%20speaking%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20plunge%20into%20a%20wild%20scheme%20brings%20them%20face%20to%20face%20with%20a%20world%20in%20which%20trigger-happy%20border%20guards%20have%20no%20qualms%20about%20snuffing%20out%20lives%20in%20the%20line%20of%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20dwelling%20on%20the%20trials%20and%20tribulations%20of%20undocumented%20immigrants%20and%20addressing%20how%20departures%2C%20destinations%20and%20displacements%20play%20out%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20illegals%2C%20the%20film%20delivers%20an%20entertaining%20yet%20sobering%20take%20on%20what%20doing%20the%20%26quot%3Bdunki%26quot%3B%20(a%20colloquial%20term%20for%20an%20unlawful%20border%20crossing)%20to%20get%20to%20Europe%20in%20search%20of%20a%20better%20life%20entails.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20parts%20of%20the%20film%20articulate%20known%20truths%20and%20come%20close%20to%20striking%20contrived%20notes%2C%20%3Ci%3EDunki%3C%2Fi%3E%20also%20has%20passages%20marked%20by%20commendable%20insight%20coupled%20with%20just%20the%20right%20mix%20of%20emotion%20and%20intelligence.%20These%20attributes%20prevent%20even%20the%20somewhat%20pat%20patterns%20of%20the%20story%20from%20undermining%20the%20overall%20impact%20of%20the%20journey%20that%20Hardy%2C%20Manu%2C%20Buggu%20and%20Balli%20undertake%20at%20grave%20risk%20to%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20might%20quibble%20that%20%3Ci%3EDunki%3C%2Fi%3E%20tends%20at%20times%20to%20not%20only%20make%20light%20of%20the%20urge%20of%20some%20to%20flee%20their%20village%20and%20country%20for%20what%2C%20from%20a%20distance%2C%20looks%20like%20greener%20pastures%20but%20also%20romanticize%20the%20misadventures%20of%20people%20desperate%20to%20bypass%20the%20visa%20system%20and%20sneak%20into%20the%20UK%20as%20a%20specious%20revolt%20against%20what%20the%20British%20did%20to%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent%20for%20a%20century.%20Mercifully%2C%20the%20characters%20-%20and%20the%20film%20-%20come%20full%20circle%20and%20hold%20out%20no%20false%20hopes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20out%20and%20out%20a%20Rajkumar%20Hirani%20film.%20It%20revels%20in%20seeing%20the%20funny%20side%20of%20the%20predicament%20of%20people%20grappling%20with%20a%20world%20where%20the%20rule%20book%20matters%20more%20than%20the%20feelings%20and%20needs%20of%20humans%2C%20where%20fences%20erected%20by%20nations%20put%20the%20poor%20who%20have%20little%20access%20to%20education%20and%20wealth%20at%20an%20insurmountable%20disadvantage%20that%20leads%20to%20desperate%20and%20often%20fatal%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20persona%20that%20Shahrukh%20Khan%20assumes%20in%20%3Ci%3EDunki%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20the%20men%20he%20played%20in%20his%20previous%20two%20releases%20of%20the%20year.%20He%20dons%20the%20garb%20of%20an%20altruistic%20trouble-shooter%20who%20risks%20death%20and%20deportation%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20as%20a%20young%20man%20left%20high%20and%20dry%20by%20the%20quirks%20of%20fate%20and%20an%20ageing%20villager%20who%20has%20been%20there%20and%20done%20that%20but%20has%20not%20lost%20his%20zest%20for%20life%2C%20he%20delivers%20an%20act%20shot%20through%20with%20oodles%20of%20charm%20and%20cheeriness.%20Taapsee%20Pannu%20is%20pitch-perfect.%20She%20matches%20SRK's%20flair%20move%20for%20move%20with%20impressive%20elan.%20No%20mean%20feat%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20memorable%20special%20appearance%2C%20Vicky%20Kaushal%20-%20he%20is%20cast%20as%20a%20man%20who%20has%20a%20pressing%20reason%20to%20seek%20a%20visa%20for%20travel%20to%20the%20UK%20-%20makes%20a%20strong%20impression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikram%20Kochhar%20and%20Anil%20Grover%20make%20the%20most%20of%20their%20roles%20in%20a%20film%20that%20(unlike%20average%20star-driven%20Bollywood%20vehicles)%20does%20not%20relegate%20them%20to%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EDunki%3C%2Fi%3E%20does%20not%20exactly%20break%20boundaries%20but%20the%20route%20that%20it%20takes%20leads%20it%20in%20the%20right%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703150340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fr4m9vppg_-dunki_625x300_21_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdunki-review-buoyed-by-flawless-performances-with-shah-rukh-khan-taapsee-pannu-leading-the-way-3-5-stars-4715441%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dunki%20Review%3A%20In%20a%20memorable%20special%20appearance%2C%20Vicky%20Kaushal%20-%20he%20is%20cast%20as%20a%20man%20who%20has%20a%20pressing%20reason%20to%20seek%20a%20visa%20for%20travel%20to%20the%20UK%20-%20makes%20a%20strong%20impression.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdunki-review-buoyed-by-flawless-performances-with-shah-rukh-khan-taapsee-pannu-leading-the-way-3-5-stars-4715441%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Myanmar%20junta%20accused%20of%20war%20crimes%20over%20response%20to%20rebel%20offensive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703150116000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106180242%2Cimgsize-1863649.cms%