28.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%E2%80%99s%20drug%20regulator%20has%20decided%20that%20an%20anti-cold%20drug%20mixture%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20231221060534%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fcdsco.gov.in%2Fopencms%2Fopencms%2Fsystem%2Fmodules%2FCDSCO.WEB%2Felements%2Fdownload_file_division.jsp%3Fnum_id%3DMTA3Nzg%3D%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cshould%20be%20not%20used%20in%20children%20below%20four%20years%20of%20age%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ordered%20that%20manufacturers%20apply%20a%20warning%20label%20to%20this%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Drugs%20Standard%20Control%20Organisation%20(CDSCO)%20asked%20state%20drug%20controllers%20on%20Monday%20(December%2018)%20to%20direct%20manufacturers%20in%20their%20respective%20jurisdictions%20to%20apply%20the%20label%20to%20the%20drug%20mixture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Rajeev%20Singh%20Raghuvanshi%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20drug%20controller%20general%20and%20head%20of%20the%20CDSCO%2C%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20based%20on%20the%20recommendations%20of%20an%20expert%20committee%20that%20met%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mixture%20in%20question%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98fixed-dose%20combination%E2%80%99%20(FDC)%20of%20chlorpheniramine%20maleate%20and%20phenylephrine%20hydrochloride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reuters%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fhealthcare-pharmaceuticals%2Findia-bans-anti-cold-drug-combination-kids-aged-under-four-2023-12-20%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20FDC%20is%20used%20in%20syrups%20and%20tablets%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20treat%20common%20cold%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECough%20syrups%20manufactured%20in%20India%20have%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20after%20the%20deaths%20of%20children%20both%20at%20home%20and%20abroad%20were%20linked%20to%20their%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20said%20that%20cough%20syrups%20made%20in%20India%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Finvestigates%2Fspecial-report%2Fhealth-coughsyrup-india%2F%5C%22%3Elinked%20to%20the%20deaths%20of%20141%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Gambia%2C%20Uzbekistan%20and%20Cameroon%20over%202022%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20agency%20also%20reported%20that%20in%20June%20this%20year%2C%20India%20announced%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fhealthcare-pharmaceuticals%2Findia-allow-cough-syrup-export-only-after-tests-govt-lab-notice-2023-05-23%2F%5C%22%3Emandate%20the%20testing%20of%20cough%20syrups%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20they%20are%20exported.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703148264000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23115348%2Fimage-1528.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fcdsco-says-anti-cold-fdc-not-to-be-used-in-children-below-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cough%20syrups%20manufactured%20in%20India%20have%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20after%20the%20deaths%20of%20children%20both%20at%20home%20and%20abroad%20were%20linked%20to%20their%20consumption.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fcdsco-says-anti-cold-fdc-not-to-be-used-in-children-below-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20man%20cleared%20of%20murder%20after%2048%20years%20in%20prison%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703148176000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F69C8%2Fproduction%2F_132108072_microsoftteams-image-17.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67782907%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Glynn%20Simmons%20says%20his%20nearly%20half-century%20in%20prison%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Blesson%20in%20resilience%20and%20tenacity%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A676%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22htt