%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20revenue%20receipts.%20Another%2035%25%20is%20being%20consumed%20by%20the%20salaries%20and%20pensions%20of%20government%20employees%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20careful%20analysis%20of%20the%20above%20facts%20shows%20that%20Telangana%2C%20which%20was%20a%20revenue%20surplus%20state%20in%202014%20and%20has%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20growing%20economies%20in%20the%20country%2C%20is%20now%20staring%20at%20a%20debt%20crisis%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Ftelangana-releases-white-paper-on-finances-state-was-revenue-surplus-in-2014-now-staring-at-debt-crisis-2478227-2023-12-20%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20blaming%20the%20previous%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20government%20for%20%E2%80%9Cfinancial%20anarchy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grim%20financial%20position%20of%20the%20state%20means%20the%20Congress%20government%20has%20an%20uphill%20task%20to%20fulfill%20its%20six%20guarantees%2C%20which%20helped%20it%20wrest%20power%20from%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20Telangana%20was%20formed%20and%20the%20BRS%20government%20took%20over%20in%202014%2C%20the%20state%20had%20a%20revenue%20surplus%20and%20was%20one%20of%20the%20fastest-growing%20economies%20in%20the%20country%20at%20that%20time%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20a%20situation%20of%20positive%20balances%20for%20all%20100%25%20of%20the%20days%20in%202014%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20the%20state%20has%20a%20positive%20balance%20in%20less%20than%2010%25%20of%20the%20days%20shows%20enormous%20fiscal%20stress%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20finance%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunching%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%20previous%20government%2C%20he%20said%20no%20tangible%20fiscal%20assets%20in%20proportion%20to%20the%20money%20spent%20were%20created%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years.%20He%20said%C2%A0as%20per%20current%20budget%20estimates%2C%20the%20debt%20will%20touch%20Rs%203.86%20lakh%20crore%20by%20the%20end%20of%20fiscal%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20White%20Paper%2C%20there%20was%20a%20gap%20of%20almost%2020%25%20between%20the%20budgeted%20and%20the%20actual%20expenditure%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%20The%20budget%20estimates%20grew%20from%20Rs%20100%2C638%20crore%20in%202014-15%20to%20Rs%20256%2C859%20crore%20in%202022-23.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20actual%20expenditure%20was%20%3Cspan%3ERs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E62%2C306%20crore%20in%202014-15%20and%20it%20went%20up%20to%C2%A0%3Cspan%3ERs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E204%2C085%20crore%20in%202022-23.%20In%20the%20period%20between%202014-23%2C%20on%20average%2C%20Telangana%20actually%20spent%20only%2082.3%25%20of%20the%20budgeted%20expenditure%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20finance%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Ftelanganas-debt-rose-10-times-under-brs-to-6-71-l-crcong-101703099707965.html%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20said%20gap%20is%20not%20only%20high%20in%20comparison%20to%20other%20states%20but%20also%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20expenditure%20achieved%20in%20united%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20gap%20in%20expenditure%20between%20the%20budget%20and%20actuals%20has%20meant%20that%20there%20is%20an%20accumulation%20of%20committed%20expenditure%20in%20terms%20of%20payments%20made%20for%20the%20services%20rendered%20by%20the%20suppliers%20and%20contractors%20and%20also%20to%20the%20employees%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20already%20existing%20committed%20expenditure%2C%20the%20Congress%20government%20has%20little%20fiscal%20room%20for%20undertaking%20a%20slew%20of%20welfare%20measures%20it%20had%20announced%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20recently%20concluded%20Assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20former%20finance%20minister%20and%20BRS%20leader%20T.%20Harish%20Rao%20dismissed%20the%20White%20Paper%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20bundle%20of%20white%20lies%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20blatant%20lie%20that%20the%20previous%20government%20had%20not%20created%20any%20tangible%20assets%20in%20tune%20with%20the%20borrowings%2C%20only%20to%20project%20that%20it%20had%20not%20done%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rao%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Ftelanganas-debt-rose-10-times-under-brs-to-6-71-l-crcong-101703099707965.html%5C%22%3Eadded%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%2C%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20party%20said%20under%20the%20BRS%20government%2C%20the%20assets%20of%20the%20state%20had%20increased%20by%20159%25.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20every%20Rs%201%20loan%20borrowed%20by%20the%20BRS%20government%2C%20there%20was%20creation%20of%20assets%20worth%20Rs%201%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Rao%2C%20the%20Congress%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20escape%20from%20its%20responsibility%20of%20implementing%20its%20six%20guarantees%20by%20showing%20a%20grim%20picture%20of%20state%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703138600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21112716%2FEffect-37.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fat-6-71-lakh-crore-debt-telangana-staring-at-a-crisis-congress-govt-releases-white-paper%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20newly%20formed%20Congress%20government%2C%20'financial%20anarchy'%20of%20the%20previous%20BRS%20government%20resulted%20in%20state's%20debt%20rise%20almost%2010%20times%20from%C2%A0Rs%2072%2C658%20crore%20in%202014-15%20to%20Rs%20671%2C757%20crore%20at%20present.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fat-6-71-lakh-crore-debt-telangana-staring-at-a-crisis-congress-govt-releases-white-paper%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tide%20turns%20for%20Channel%20smugglers%20but%20the%2