167%2Fmental-health-motherhood-swagata-majumdar-started-child-loss-support-group-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eneonatal%20care%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20the%20snake%20bite%20ward%20is%20of%20prime%20importance.%20Elaborating%20on%20the%20reason%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CHingalganj%20is%20in%20such%20a%20remote%20area.%20Government%20facilities%20are%20not%20enough%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20people.%20The%20Sundarbans%20are%20popular%20for%20their%20biodiversity%2C%20which%20includes%20snakes%2C%20so%20snake%20bite%20cases%20are%20very%20common.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20government%20arranging%20anti-venom%20facilities%2C%20the%20doctor%20shares%20that%20these%20are%20insufficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20experience%2C%20I%20have%20witnessed%2030%20people%20dying%20of%20snake%20bites%20every%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%20One%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332088%2Fmugdha-pradhan-ithrive-functional-medicine-mental-health-physical-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20etched%20in%20his%20memory.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20attended%20a%20marriage%20in%20the%20village.%20Two%20days%20after%20the%20wedding%2C%20the%20young%20bride%20of%2018%20was%20sleeping%20outside%20the%20house%20when%20a%20snake%20bit%20her.%20There%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20any%20anti-venom%20available%20and%20she%20died.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EService%20rooted%20in%20love%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201707px)%20100vw%2C%201707px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FVG5_0902_11zon-1700740226-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Arunoday%20Mondal%20receiving%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20in%202020%5C%22